sequenceDiagram
  participant P as Patient
  participant A as Aretide
  participant B as Beluga

  P->>A: POST /api/refills/same-dose/
  A->>B: POST REFILL_ENDPOINT masterId medId
  alt NEW_RX_SENT
    B-->>A: sync NEW_RX_SENT
    A->>A: RefillRequest approved
    B->>A: webhook PHARMACY_ORDER_SHIPPED
    B->>A: webhook PACKAGE_DELIVERED
  else NEEDS_CHECKIN
    B-->>A: sync pending
    A->>A: RefillRequest pending
  else denied
    B-->>A: sync denied
    A->>A: RefillRequest denied
  end
